Design patterns: The design patterns are well-proved solutions for solving the 
===============  particular/specific problem statement or task.

Problem Statement-1: let consider we want to create a class for which only one instance/object
-------------------  should be created and that instance/object can shared among the other classes.

Singleton design pattern(Creational Design Pattern)

Rules to create Singleton Object:
================================

1. declare static fields
2. make the constructor scope as private
3. create static factory method

